    <section>
<h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>Developed in Unreal Engine 4</p> 
         <p>A prototype and final year project, experimenting with level design, camera cuts, VFX and more.</p>
       
        
    </section>
    <!--Responsibilities section-->
    <section>
      <h2>Responsibilities</h2>
      <ul>
          <l>Creating all assets</l>
          <l>Game & Level Design.</l>
          <l>Prototyping and implementing all mechanics</l>
           <l>UI/UX Design/implementation. </l>
        
        
      </ul>
    </section>
<!--Story section-->
    <section>
      <h2>Synopsis/Demo</h2>
      
    <p>The player must push iceblocks into the gaps to form walkways, in doing so they can light the lanterns and exit the cave.</p>
    
    
      
    </section>
<!--Skills developed section-->
    <section>
      <h2>New Skills Developed</h2>
      <ul>
        <l>Unreal Engine 4's physics system.</l>
        <l>Post processing and other VFX using cascade.</l>
        <l>level design.</l>

      </ul>
    </section>

